Program: Last Word
Title: James Garner, Joep Lange, Alan Alan, Philip Wayre, Dora Bryan
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04b2wzx
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Jul 2014
On Last Word this week: James Garner, the film and television actor who starred in Maverick and the Rockford Files.... The Dutch physician, Joep Lange, who's regarded as one of the world's top clinical AIDS researchers.... Alan Alan, an escapologist described as Britain's answer to Houdini.... Philip Wayre, a naturalist who's credited with saving the otter from extinction in England.... And the Bafta award winning actress, Dora Bryan, whose career embraced the stage, screen and television. Show less